			<div class="pricing-page-section">
                <h2>Support &amp; SLA</h2>
                <p>If you have any questions or need help, please visit <a href="/support/contact/" id="networking-contact-page">Azure Support</a> and select self-help service or any other method to contact us for support.</p>
				
				<p>The virtual network is free of charge and doesn’t provide service level agreements. To learn more about the details of our service level agreement, please visit the <a href="/support/legal/sla/" id="pricing_virtual-networking_sla">Service Level Agreements</a> page.</p>
				
